---
// Benefits.astro
const benefits = [
  "Reduce el tiempo de cierre de ventas en un 40%",
  "Mejora la experiencia del cliente comprador",
  "Proyecta una imagen altamente profesional de tu desarrollo",
  "Facilita y moderniza el trabajo de tu equipo comercial",
  "Centraliza planos, renders y documentos, eliminando el desorden",
  "Aumenta confianza del cliente"
];
---
<section id="beneficios" class="py-24 bg-primary text-theme-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">
          Un retorno de inversión que tus vendedores agradecerán
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          No solo estás comprando software. Estás adquiriendo un proceso comercial optimizado, mayor fluidez operativa y una inigualable percepción de valor por parte del comprador final.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-5">
          {benefits.map(benefit => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="mt-1 shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-quaternary border border-secondary flex items-center justify-center text-theme-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-secondary text-lg">{benefit}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="relative w-full h-full rounded-2xl bg-primary border border-quaternary overflow-hidden min-h-[400px]">
         <!-- Simple abstract chart / illustration showing growth -->
         <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-tr from-quaternary/50 to-primary z-0"></div>
         <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-64 bg-primary/50 border-t border-quaternary backdrop-blur z-10 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
             <div class="flex items-end gap-3 h-32">
                 <div class="w-1/6 bg-quaternary/40 rounded-t-md h-12"></div>
                 <div class="w-1/6 bg-quaternary/40 rounded-t-md h-20"></div>
                 <div class="w-1/6 bg-quaternary/60 rounded-t-md h-24"></div>
                 <div class="w-1/6 bg-tertiary rounded-t-md h-32 shadow-[0_-10px_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]"></div>
                 <div class="w-1/6 bg-theme-white rounded-t-md h-40 shadow-[0_-15px_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)] relative">
                    <span class="absolute -top-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 font-bold text-primary bg-theme-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs border border-secondary">+40% Leads</span>
                 </div>
                 <div class="w-1/6 bg-secondary rounded-t-md h-48"></div>
             </div>
             <p class="text-center font-mono text-xs text-secondary mt-4 border-t border-quaternary pt-4">Tasa de conversión y agilidad comercial</p>
         </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
